query:
SELECT s.id as studentId, s.registrationNumber, se.subjectId, se.userId as professorId, sub.name as subjectName
FROM students s
INNER JOIN subjectEnrollments se ON se.studentId = s.id
INNER JOIN subjects sub ON sub.id = se.subjectId
LIMIT 10;
